=Description=

"CICOLAB — is a peer-to-peer mutual support community for “exopreneurs”: misfit entrepreneurs who are solving adaptive challenges (which go far beyond “complex problems” that can be solved by technical fixes, to wicked messes that are coupled with a high degree of social complexity) that do not lend themselves to easy solutions. This paper goes into detail about the unique nature of exopreneurs and explains why a network of us working together to bootstrap our efforts could be profoundly transformative, both for ourselves and for the world at large."
